<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>경제책 읽기 프로젝트 6개월 — 책온</title>
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.png">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@supabase/supabase-js@2"></script>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+KR:wght@400;600;700;900&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap');

  :root {
    --gold: #C9A84C;
    --gold-light: #E8C96A;
    --gold-pale: #F5E9C8;
    --ink: #1A1A2E;
    --ink-mid: #2D2D4A;
    --cream: #FAF7F0;
    --warm-white: #FFFEF9;
    --text-body: #3A3A52;
    --text-muted: #8A8AA0;
    --border: #E5DFC8;
    --step1: #4A7C59;
    --step2: #7C5B2E;
    --step3: #2E4A7C;
    --month-bg-1: #F0F7F2;
    --month-bg-2: #F7F2EC;
    --month-bg-3: #EEF2F9;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; background: var(--cream); color: var(--text-body); line-height: 1.6; }

  header { background: var(--ink); position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold); }
  .header-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 14px 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 16px; }
  .logo { font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: -0.02em; text-decoration: none; }
  .logo span { color: #fff; font-weight: 300; font-size: 0.75rem; display: block; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-top: -2px; }
  nav { display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  nav button { background: none; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.4); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.82rem; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; transition: all 0.2s; }
  nav button:hover, nav button.active { background: var(--gold); border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--ink); font-weight: 700; }

  .hero { background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--ink) 0%, var(--ink-mid) 60%, #1A2744 100%); padding: 64px 24px 52px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(201,168,76,0.12) 0%, transparent 65%); }
  .hero-eyebrow { font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--gold); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px; position: relative; }
  .hero h1 { font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem); font-weight: 900; color: #fff; line-height: 1.2; position: relative; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .hero h1 em { color: var(--gold); font-style: normal; }
  .hero-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); font-size: 0.92rem; margin-bottom: 36px; position: relative; }
  .hero-steps { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 0; position: relative; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .hero-step { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .hero-step-box { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.35); border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 22px; text-align: center; }
  .hero-step-num { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .hero-step-label { font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #fff; font-weight: 700; }
  .hero-step-desc { font-size: 0.72rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top: 3px; }
  .arrow-sep { color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.2rem; padding: 0 8px; margin-top: 4px; }

  .view-bar { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 28px 24px 0; display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .view-bar-label { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-right: 4px; }
  .view-btn { padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 22px; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); background: white; font-size: 0.85rem; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; color: var(--text-body); transition: all 0.18s; font-weight: 500; }
  .view-btn:hover { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }
  .view-btn.active { background: var(--ink); border-color: var(--ink); color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; }

  .main-content { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 28px 24px 64px; }

  .books-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
  .book-card { background: white; border-radius: 14px; border: 1px solid var(--border); overflow: hidden; transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }
  .book-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(26,26,46,0.12); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .book-card-header { padding: 20px 20px 16px; display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .book-month-badge { min-width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 10px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .book-month-badge span { font-size: 0.55rem; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 1px; }
  .step1-color { background: var(--month-bg-1); color: var(--step1); }
  .step2-color { background: var(--month-bg-2); color: var(--step2); }
  .step3-color { background: var(--month-bg-3); color: var(--step3); }
  .book-meta { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .book-step-tag { font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .tag-step1 { background: var(--month-bg-1); color: var(--step1); }
  .tag-step2 { background: var(--month-bg-2); color: var(--step2); }
  .tag-step3 { background: var(--month-bg-3); color: var(--step3); }
  .book-title { font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .book-author { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .book-theme { padding: 0 20px 14px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-body); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-style: italic; }
  .book-posts { padding: 14px 20px; }
  .book-posts-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .book-posts-title { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); }
  .add-post-btn { font-size: 0.75rem; background: var(--gold); color: var(--ink); border: none; padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 16px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 700; font-family: inherit; transition: background 0.15s; }
  .add-post-btn:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }
  .post-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .post-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 8px 10px; border-radius: 8px; background: var(--cream); cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.15s; }
  .post-item:hover { background: var(--gold-pale); }
  .post-avatar { width: 26px; height: 26px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--ink); color: var(--gold); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .post-info { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .post-name { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); }
  .post-excerpt { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text-muted); white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
  .post-date { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--text-muted); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .empty-posts { text-align: center; padding: 16px; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.8rem; }
  .empty-posts span { display: block; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }

  .member-select-bar { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 28px; padding: 16px 20px; background: white; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); align-items: center; }
  .member-select-label { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-muted); width: 100%; }
  .member-chip { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; padding: 7px 14px 7px 8px; border-radius: 22px; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); background: var(--cream); cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.82rem; font-family: inherit; transition: all 0.15s; color: var(--text-body); }
  .member-chip:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }
  .member-chip.selected { background: var(--ink); border-color: var(--ink); color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; }
  .member-chip .chip-avatar { width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--gold); color: var(--ink); font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 900; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }

  .member-progress { background: white; border-radius: 14px; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .member-progress-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .member-big-avatar { width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--ink); color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 900; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; border: 2px solid var(--gold); }
  .member-name-block { flex: 1; }
  .member-name { font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); }
  .member-stat { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2px; }
  .member-stat strong { color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; }
  .progress-bar-wrap { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .progress-label { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 5px; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .progress-label strong { color: var(--ink); }
  .progress-track { height: 8px; border-radius: 4px; background: var(--border); overflow: hidden; }
  .progress-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--gold-light)); transition: width 0.5s ease; }

  .member-books-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
  .member-book-row { background: white; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 18px; transition: box-shadow 0.15s; }
  .member-book-row:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(26,26,46,0.08); }
  .member-book-row-header { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .member-post-area { background: var(--cream); border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 14px; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.15s; border: 1px dashed var(--border); }
  .member-post-area:hover { background: var(--gold-pale); border-color: var(--gold); }
  .member-post-area.has-post { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-style: solid; }
  .member-post-title { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .member-post-body { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-body); line-height: 1.55; }
  .member-post-empty { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); text-align: center; padding: 6px 0; }

  .modal-overlay { display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(26,26,46,0.65); z-index: 200; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 20px; }
  .modal-overlay.open { display: flex; }
  .modal { background: white; border-radius: 18px; max-width: 520px; width: 100%; max-height: 90vh; overflow-y: auto; box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(26,26,46,0.25); }
  .modal-header { padding: 24px 24px 0; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .modal-title { font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); }
  .modal-sub { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 3px; }
  .modal-close { background: none; border: none; font-size: 1.4rem; cursor: pointer; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1; padding: 0 4px; }
  .modal-close:hover { color: var(--ink); }
  .modal-body { padding: 20px 24px 24px; }
  .field-group { margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .field-label { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 6px; display: block; }
  .field-input, .field-textarea { width: 100%; padding: 10px 14px; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--ink); background: var(--cream); transition: border-color 0.15s; outline: none; resize: vertical; }
  .field-input:focus, .field-textarea:focus { border-color: var(--gold); background: white; }
  .field-textarea { min-height: 120px; }
  .modal-actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: flex-end; margin-top: 20px; }
  .btn-cancel { padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); background: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-body); }
  .btn-submit { padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 8px; border: none; background: var(--ink); cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; }
  .btn-submit:hover { background: var(--ink-mid); }
  .btn-submit:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; }

  .post-detail-content { padding: 20px 24px 24px; }
  .post-detail-meta { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-bottom: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .post-detail-author { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--ink); }
  .post-detail-book { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .post-detail-date { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-left: auto; }
  .post-detail-title { font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .post-detail-body { font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-body); white-space: pre-wrap; }
  .post-detail-delete { margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; }
  .btn-delete { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #999; background: none; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; }
  .btn-delete:hover { color: #e05; border-color: #e05; }

  .loading-spinner { text-align: center; padding: 40px; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .toast { position: fixed; bottom: 28px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: var(--ink); color: var(--gold); padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 24px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; z-index: 999; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s; pointer-events: none; }
  .toast.show { opacity: 1; }

  footer { background: var(--ink); padding: 28px 24px; text-align: center; }
  .footer-logo { font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  footer p { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero { padding: 44px 16px 36px; }
    .hero-steps { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
    .arrow-sep { transform: rotate(90deg); }
    .books-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .member-books-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <a href="#" class="logo">책온 경제 프로젝트 <span>BOOK TEMPERATURE × ECONOMY</span></a>
    <nav>
      <button onclick="setView('books')" id="nav-books" class="active">📚 책별 보기</button>
      <button onclick="setView('members')" id="nav-members">👤 멤버별 보기</button>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">책온 × 6개월 여정</div>
  <h1>경제책 읽기 <em>프로젝트</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">6권의 책으로 완성하는 경제적 사고와 나만의 투자 원칙</p>
  <div class="hero-steps">
    <div class="hero-step">
      <div class="hero-step-box">
        <div class="hero-step-num">Step 1 · 1–2개월</div>
        <div class="hero-step-label">경제 문맹 탈출</div>
        <div class="hero-step-desc">지식을 쌓고 가치관을 세우기</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="arrow-sep">→</div>
    <div class="hero-step">
      <div class="hero-step-box">
        <div class="hero-step-num">Step 2 · 3–4개월</div>
        <div class="hero-step-label">투자 가치관 설립</div>
        <div class="hero-step-desc">좋은 기업을 보는 눈 기르기</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="arrow-sep">→</div>
    <div class="hero-step">
      <div class="hero-step-box">
        <div class="hero-step-num">Step 3 · 5–6개월</div>
